\n<br />\n就係無論大陸定本地啲有錢人 <br />\n因為以前大陸開廠/有勢力既緣故<br />\n買撚晒啲樓黎投資<br />\n不斷推高樓價同租金 <br />\n日常生活亦愈黎愈貴<br />\n拉撚晒佢地班人/立到條法 <br />\n<br />\n班撚樣仲唔即刻賣翻走啲樓移民<br />\n咁樓價同租金仲會唔跌？<br />\n跌幾多 買唔買到睇你儲幾多錢啦<br />\n但好肯定呢條例既威力大過搞咩空置稅 印花稅"},{"pid":"adb695561d5eea51cb3deb304b0aa3f384152dd3","tid":1137484,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbe0481f1fd0161ab66dc8efa86d4b7582314c25","tid":1137484,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a62cdd58ba132d22fc3dfe2a94621f8dc8c3e369","tid":1137484,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"ab82465356678551579edcc4ab5df7ed6251f696","tid":1137484,"uid":78947,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T21:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E63zT9E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE63zT9E.png&h=668f6519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資產階級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T21:03:26.000Z","msg":"笑死 原來佢準備買樓<br />\n我係佢個post留過言 不過佢當我五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係果句啦 我完全同中國大陸無交集<br />\n完全唔怕會比人拉上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T21:08:32.000Z","msg":"可能佢啱啱落咗訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T21:12:16.000Z","msg":"似啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚真係立到 到時好似寶星咁跌翻幾個月<br />\n嚇都嚇死"},{"pid":"7317a8299fd248b5baf5d14389a2336527d86202","tid":1137484,"uid":2679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T21:15:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母樓主快撚啲上水回應啦<br />\n開個post cap人地兩句就潛水<br />\n祝你撻訂蝕撚晒啲錢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa731fb8c816f1cc09ed4fa335314ac180a50bd","